Job Posting Title:   SE_Business Consultant_Lead
Description:

Business Consultant contribute to projects or programs primarily with process and/or functional skills, often connected to IT solutions and Process & IT implementation. Business Consulting encompasses in all project phases from pre-studies to implementation of change and provide process and/or functional expertise and best practice.Lead level is a specialist in Project Management & Support, typically obtained through education and work experience. Responsibilities typically include:
- Managing large projects or (end to end) processes with limited oversight from manager.
- Coaching, reviewing and delegating work to lower level professionals.
- Problems faced are difficult and often complex.


Lead: position typically requires 8 years or more relevant experience

